  Locus:
    Page: 58
    Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Children
---
A child is not your ego, it is not a pet dog in the house, it is not a
substitute for love. A child has nothing to do with that. A child is born
to you so that you can prepare him to face time unto eternity.
